advertisments:
--------------
If you like Tippometer try to get the other projects of the authors!!

MUIMousoMeter by Wolfgang and Michael:
    Like TippoMeter but meassures mousemovement and checks mousebuttons.

ARose by Wolfgang and Michael:
    Screenblanker module for Garshne and BlitzBlank. Draws very nice 
    circlefigures. Looks best on GFX-boards with 800x600x256 Colormode.
    (eg. Picasso-II, Cybergraphics)

D.E.R. ST-Player (STP) © Wolfgang Breyha
    A Soundtracker-Moduleplayer with a GUI like a real CD-Player.
    Many features like nonstop playing, random, programmable.

